name: SELLING HOPE$
description:
Red light, green light! Stop!! 
Minting, minting, Stop!! 

Do we live in a 'Squid Game' but in NFT way? Trying so hard to collect that coins and figuring out the best stategies to survive. So, who will be the winner? What are the best stategies? Nobody knows.

Many people think that selling art on NFT is easy money, but in reality it's not.  In the end they despair because it is not what they expected.
